<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>SoftsKILLER</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/index.css">
  </head>
  <body> 
    <div class="container">
     <div class="card border-0 shadow my-5">
      <div class="card-body p-5">
      <br>
        <div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert">
          <h3><%= name %> was born to DIE!</h3>           
        </div>

        <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-sm-12"></div>
              <%= say%>
            </div>
        </div>

            <div class='row'>
                <div class='col-sm-8'>
                    <ul>
                        <li class="list-unstyled">
                          <label class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Health</label> 
                          <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= get('health') %>%" aria-valuenow="<%= get('health') %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= get('health') %></div>
        </div>

                </li>
                <li class="list-unstyled">
                    <label class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Horror</label> 
                            <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= get('horror') %>%" aria-valuenow="<%= get('horror') %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= get('horror') %></div>
        </div>

                </li>
                <li class="list-unstyled">
                    <label class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Calm</label> 
                            <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= get('calm') %>%" aria-valuenow="<%= get('calm') %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= get('calm') %></div>
        </div>

                </li>
                <li class="list-unstyled">
                    <label class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Die</label> 
                            <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= get('die') %>%" aria-valuenow="<%= get('die') %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= get('die') %></div>
        </div>

                </li>
            
          </ul>
            </div>
              <div class='col-sm-4'>
                <img src= "<%=image%>" class="img-fluid" alt="Responsive image">
              </div>
            </div>
            <br>
            <hr>
            <div class='row'>
                  <form action="/watch" method="get">
                     <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="watch" value="watch">Watch a horror movie</button>
                  </form>

                  <form action="/relax" method="get">
                     <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="relax" value="relax">Try to calm</button>
                  </form>

                  <form action="/psycho" method="get">
                     <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="psycho" value="psycho">We should go to the doctor!</button>
                  </form>

                  <form action="/died" method="get">
                     <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="died" value="died">I know the best way to die for you!</button>
                  </form>

                 
                  <button class="btn btn-success" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseExample" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">HELP</button>
                    <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
                      <div class="card card-body bg-light">
                        <p>If you use a 'watch' action, then you will improve his <strong>horror</strong>, but decrease <strong>health, calm</strong> and increase <strong>die</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'relax' action, then you will improve his <strong>health</strong>, <strong>calm</strong> but increase <strong>die</strong> and <strong>horror too</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'psycho' action, then you will improve his <strong>health</strong> but decreases <strong>calm</strong> and <strong>die with horror</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'died' action, then you will improve <strong>die and horror</strong>but decreases <strong>calm and health</strong> .</p>
                      </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
       </div>
    </body>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.3/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ZMP7rVo3mIykV+2+9J3UJ46jBk0WLaUAdn689aCwoqbBJiSnjAK/l8WvCWPIPm49" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-ChfqqxuZUCnJSK3+MXmPNIyE6ZbWh2IMqE241rYiqJxyMiZ6OW/JmZQ5stwEULTy" crossorigin="anonymous"></script></body>
</html>
